cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper discusses feature learning with deep models for vision tasks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The applications of the proposed method are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
